name: Paprika Puffball Dress With Tags
description:
This is a really cute little black dress made by Paprika, and is in a puffball style.
It is a size small so it will probably fit sizes 6 to a small 10.
It is brand new, with the tags still on, at an RRP of £35 in shops.
Perfect for any occassion, and everyday wear.
If you want any more pictures, or any extra measurements, please contact me :)

name: Paprika One Strap Bow Detail Dress With Tags
description:
This is a brand new dress made by Paprika. 
It says it is a size small, but it would probably fit a size 6 to a small size 10.
This is a gorgeous little black dress, perfect for special occassions or clubbing, as it is very versatile.
It has one strap in in silky black material with a big bow on it.
It is at an RRP of £35 in shops currently.
If you require any more pictures or extra measurements then feel free to contact me :)

name: CUSTOM CUTIES!
description:
I currently don't have any custom items up on here, as I would like you to tell me what sort of items you would like!
I can do custom strap tops, t-shirts, necklaces, bracelets, or detailing for you to put on your own clothing. Any other ideas are welcome also!
Just let me know in an email what sort of thing you would like and I will email back letting you know if it will be possible or not.
I can get most sizes in t-shirts and strap tops and most colours also, and will do them at a reasonable price aswell, probably for around, or less than £10, depending on the amount of time, skill, material and bits and bobs needed for the job.
Please let me know what you think and any ideas are definitely welcome. 
Thank you! :)

name: Madam Rage Multi Coloured Dress With Tags
description:
This is a beautifully brightly coloured dress by Madam Rage.
On the label it says size 10, but I'm a size 6/8 and it fits me just fine! So I would say it fits between an 8 and a 10 best, probably a small 12.
It is brand new, and has adjustable spaghetti straps and two layers; the top brightly coloured layer attached to the straps, and a tighter black layer underneath which just shows at the bottom of the dress. It has a really nice contrast between the flowing top layer, and the tighter bottom layer.
It is retailing in shops at an RRP of £20.
If any extra pictures or measurements are required, please let me know, I'll be happy to help :)
